WorkItem.Description:
I'm getting an error when Chirpy tries to generate files from Bootstrap 2.0.2 that is currently available from Initializr.com. 

Error	88	Fatal error, cannot continue: null cannot be converted to an object

Error	88	Expected '}' on line 305 in file 'bootstrap/mixins.less':
[304]:   opacity: @opacity / 100;
[305]:    filter: ~"alpha(opacity=@{opacity})";
       ---^
[306]: }	

If I simply delete line 305, another error is raised on the next line with a "filter" element.

It could be related to this: https://github.com/dotless/dotless/issues/155
